MovieDB
A simple and elegant movie search website that uses the OMDB API to fetch movie details. Built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, this project features a cinematic design with a dark theme, centered movie details, and a responsive layout.

Features
Movie Search: Search for movies by title with autocomplete suggestions as you type.
Detailed Information: Displays movie details including poster, title, year, rating, genre, writer, actors, plot, language, and awards.
Responsive Design: Optimized for both desktop and mobile devices with a centered layout.
Cinematic Theme: Dark background with a subtle cinema-related image, a red accent color (#e50914), and a professional look.
Loading Spinner: Visual feedback during API calls to enhance user experience.
